ascade deletion works via ownerReferences\n- [ ] **5.4** Handle stuck resources that fail to delete — force delete after grace period expires\n\n---\n\n## Phase 6: Periodic Sync\n\n- [ ] **6.1** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/sync.go` — implement periodic reconciliation\n- [ ] **6.2** Add sync interval configuration (default 30s) to config\n- [ ] **6.3** Implement `syncAllSandboxes` — scan and reconcile all Sandboxes\n- [ ] **6.4** Add drift detection — compare desired state vs actual cluster state\n- [ ] **6.5** Implement `repairDrift` — fix any state mismatches\n\n---\n\n## Phase 7: Status & Conditions\n\n- [ ] **7.1** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/status.go` — implement `updateStatusConditions`\n- [ ] **7.2** Implement Pod status sync — map Pod conditions to Sandbox conditions\n- [ ] **7.3** Implement status phase management — Pending/Running/Succeeded/Failed/Unknown\n- [ ] **7.4** Add `setStatusPhase(phase)` helper\n- [ ] **7.5** Add condition helpers: `setCondition(type, status, reason, message)`\n\n---\n\n## Phase 8: Error Handling & Retry\n\n- [ ] **8.1** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/errors.go` — define reconciler error types\n- [ ] **8.2** Implement exponential backoff retry in `reconcileWithRetry`\n- [ ] **8.3** Handle transient errors: retry up to 5 times\n- [ ] **8.4** Handle permanent errors: set Failed status, emit event, no retry\n- [ ] **8.5** Implement conflict handling: fetch latest, re-apply\n\n---\n\n## Phase 9: Event Recording\n\n- [ ] **9.1** Integrate k8s event recorder in Reconciler\n- [ ] **9.2** Emit events for: Create success/failure, Update, Delete, Retry\n- [ ] **9.3** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/events.go` — event emission helpers\n- [ ] **9.4** Add event filtering to avoid duplicate events\n\n---\n\n## Phase 10: Workqueue & Rate Limiting\n\n- [ ] **10.1** Setup workqueue with rate limiting in `SetupWithManager`\n- [ ] **10.2** Configure bucket4j rate limiter: burst 10, rate 10 QPS\n- [ ] **10.3** Implement priority: delete > update > create\n- [ ] **10.4** Add namespace-scoped rate limiting\n- [ ] **10.5** Implement max concurrent reconciles per namespace (default 10)\n\n---\n\n## Phase 11: Metrics & Observability\n\n- [ ] **11.1** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/metrics.go` — define Prometheus metrics\n- [ ] **11.2** Add `sandbox_reconcile_total` counter with labels\n- [ ] **11.3** Add `sandbox_reconcile_duration_seconds` histogram\n- [ ] **11.4** Add `sandbox_reconcile_retries_total` counter\n- [ ] **11.5** Add `sandbox_workqueue_depth` gauge\n- [ ] **11.6** Expose metrics endpoint in workloadmanager\n\n---\n\n## Phase 12: Health Checks\n\n- [ ] **12.1** Implement `/healthz/reconciler` health check endpoint\n- [ ] **12.2** Check informer sync status\n- [ ] **12.3** Report workqueue depth\n- [ ] **12.4** Report last reconciliation timestamp\n\n---\n\n## Phase 13: Unit Tests\n\n- [ ] **13.1** `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/create_test.go` — TestReconcileCreate_Success\n- [ ] **13.2** `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/create_test.go` — TestReconcileCreate_PodCreation\n- [ ] **13.3** `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/create_test.go` — TestReconcileCreate_ServiceCreation\n- [ ] **13.4** `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/update_test.go` — TestReconcileUpdate_DetectChanges\n- [ ] **13.5** `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/update_test.go` — TestReconcileUpdate_PodPatch\n- [ ] **13.6** `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/delete_test.go` — TestReconcileDelete_Cleanup\n- [ ] **13.7** `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/status_test.go` — TestStatusSync_PodToSandbox\n- [ ] **13.8** `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/status_test.go` — TestStatusConditions\n- [ ] **13.9** `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/error_test.go` — TestRetryWithBackoff\n- [ ] **13.10** `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/error_test.go` — TestPermanentError_NoRetry\n- [ ] **13.11** `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/sync_test.go` — TestPeriodicSync\n\n---\n\n## Phase 14: Integration Tests\n\n- [ ] **14.1** `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/e2e_test.go` — E2E create sandbox and verify Pod created\n- [ ] **14.2** E2E update sandbox spec and verify Pod updated\n- [ ] **14.3** E2E delete sandbox and verify owned resources cleaned up\n- [ ] **14.4** E2E reconcile failure and verify status updated to Failed\n\n---\n\n## Phase 15: Verification\n\n- [ ] **15.1** `go build ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` — successful compilation\n- [ ] **15.2** `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/...` — all unit tests pass\n- [ ] **15.3** `go test -race ./pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/...` — no race conditions\n- [ ] **15.4** `go vet ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` — no issues\n- [ ] **15.5** `golangci-lint run ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` — linter passes\n- [ ] **15.6** Test coverage > 50% (`go test -coverprofile=c.out ./pkg/workloadmanager/...`)\n\n---\n\n## Dependency Graph\n\n| Task | Depends On |\n|------|------------|\n| Phase 1 | — (standalone) |\n| Phase 2 | Phase 1 |\n| Phase 3 | Phase 2 |\n| Phase 4 | Phase 3 |\n| Phase 5 | Phase 2 |\n| Phase 6 | Phase 3 |\n| Phase 7 | Phase 3, Phase 4 |\n| Phase 8 | Phase 3-7 |\n| Phase 9 | Phase 1 |\n| Phase 10 | Phase 1 |\n| Phase 11 | Phase 1 |\n| Phase 12 | Phase 1 |\n| Phase 13 | Phase 1-12 |\n| Phase 14 | Phase 13 |\n| Phase 15 | Phase 13-14 |\n\n---\n\n## References\n\n- Delta Spec: `changes/AR-007/delta-spec.md`\n- Design: ST-3 completed (Implementation Ready)\n- Related AR: AR-005 (Sandbox 创建处理器), AR-006 (Sandbox 删除与生命周期管理)\n- Kubernetes Controller Runtime: https://book.kubebuilder.io/","additions":1,"deletions":1},"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-007/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775845168364,"end":1775845168373}}}}
